Q: Cessna Citation Encore+机型的座位数是多少？
SQL: SELECT DISTINCT seat_num FROM aircraft_details WHERE aircraft_model_name = "Cessna Citation Encore+";
actual_SQL:
SELECT aircraft_model_name,
       seat_num
FROM aircraft_details
WHERE aircraft_model_name IN ('Cessna Citation X',
                              'Cessna Citation Encore',
                              'Cessna Citation I',
                              'Cessna Citation Encore+',
                              'Cessna Citation V',
                              'Cessna Citation X+')
LIMIT 50;
